content_request: je veux le volume du trafic data sur le réseau 4G en avril 2025

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT
    monthly_data.year AS year,
    monthly_data.month AS month,
    SUM(monthly_data.trafic_4g_mo) AS total_trafic_4g_mo
FROM
    monthly_data
WHERE
    monthly_data.year = 2025
    AND monthly_data.month = 4
GROUP BY
    monthly_data.year,
    monthly_data.month
ORDER BY
    monthly_data.year DESC,
    monthly_data.month DESC;
